ảo thu ký đề Thiên Trúc Linh Ẩn tự - 早秋寄題天竺靈隱寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-%C4%90%E1%BA%A3o/author-zlEhGhvit8FPpDIsa8T0QA">Giả Đảo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BB%93-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Nguy%C3%AAn/T%E1%BB%AB-Thi%E1%BB%83m-T%C3%A2y-Nho-h%E1%BB%8Dc-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-c%E1%BB%AD-nh%C3%A0n-c%C6%B0-ng%C3%B4n-ch%C3%AD/poem-PSR1uQO_UnVPoC0A-ZZX9g">Từ Thiểm Tây Nho học đề cử nhàn cư ngôn chí - 辭陝西儒學提舉閒居言志</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BB%93-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-vNqjO3qn_lddcLSXVQdpGA">Bồ Đạo Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Trang/V%C4%83n-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-4WVTiy0CZySyBGB5qiMWVQ">Văn địch - 聞笛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Trang/author-QKy6LHJMqAcMRcgSw6RXSA">Lưu Khắc Trang</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ung-%C4%90%C3%A0o/V%C4%83n-%C4%91%E1%BB%97-quy%C3%AAn-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-LHTjVHiLvstHxFiRvk1VUA">Văn đỗ quyên kỳ 1 - 聞杜鵑其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ung-%C4%90%C3%A0o/author-54CdLotgLgjZolehyx7oYw">Ung Đào</a>)<br></div>	</div>
